The Prints sizes available are A4, A5, 8x10 and 5x7 and 4x6 Inches or Emailed.

and can be printed on Matt, Satin, or Gloss. IF you can't decide I have listed the benefits of each.

Gloss — gloss coated paper has a high sheen. Gloss papers have less bulk and opacity and are typically less expensive than dull & matte paper of equal thickness. Gloss coatings reduce ink absorption, which give the sheet an excellent color definition.

Satin — a satin coating is a less shiny coated finish. It has a lower gloss level than gloss finish, yet a higher gloss level than matte finish. Colors are sharp and vivid.

Matte — a matte coated paper is a non-glossy, flat looking paper with very little sheen. Matte papers are more opaque, contain greater bulk, and are higher in cost. The coating still keeps much of the ink from being absorbed by the paper, which produces excellent, vibrant color.

results.title: Under the Drusy Moon, cobalt calcite drusy Pendant, Lemon Chacedony Pendant, Burnt Fire Agate Pendant, 3 pendant necklace, statement piece
results.description: This 3 piece pendant is definitely one-of-a-kind.  Cobalt Calcite Druzy (Pink), Lemon Chalcedony (yellow-green) and Fire agate (black and white), are each suspended on silver pendants from one 5" heavy silver wire, which is attached to silver rolo chain.  There are three words stamped into the backs of the pendants (one word per pendant), LIVE, LOVE, LAUGH.  the total length of the piece is 17.5 inches, and can be cinched up to the second ring, which is at 16".  Cobalt Calcite Druzy is truly a stunning and sparkling stone, and this one has a circumference of 1".  I make variations of this type of necklace, but no two are alike, as these stones cannot be found in bulk, but I carefully pick and chose these stones, which have been cut by lapidary artists.  As in so many of my pieces, the way this piece is designed is the pendants are all suspended together, but can move independent of each other, to create interest.

results.title: Stackable Love Live Laugh Midi Rings, Stamped Adjustable Knuckle Rings. Set of Three Midi Rings,  Stamped Aluminum Midi Rings
results.description:
Love, Live, Laugh are words to live by!

This set of three stackable midi rings lets the world know how you feel.

This set of knuckle rings are approximately US size 3.5 but I can tailor them to fit whatever finger that you wish to wear them on.

A general rule of thumb is that a midi ring will be 3-4 sizes smaller than your normal size. For example, if you are a size 7 on your middle finger, you should take a size 4 in midi ring.

Midi rings are rings that sits on your finger above the lower knuckle. While the trend sounds limiting, there are actually a ton of ways to own this midi ring look! In this example, the model is wearing midi rings as her primary jewelry staple. We love how she has one on almost every finger to create a line effect.
